Package hu.klenium.tetris

Contains the Tetris game logic, which is independ of views and user inputs.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Board
    Board is a grid, it stores the fallen tetrominoes' parts.
    Main
    Entry point of the Java programme.
    TetrisGame
    Stores and controls a game's state, manages its components.
    Tetromino
    A shape in Tetris game, which can be controlled by the player.
    TetrominoData
    Helper data structure that stores all informations of a tetromino's parts in a specificed rotation.
    TetrominoDataFactory
    Constructs data for tetrominoes.
    TetrominoPart
    Helper data structure that stores one tetromino part/cell's data.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    UserCommand
    A command is an event type, caused by the game's player to control the falling tetromino.
